column2: SELECT  g.objid, g.specobjid, sp.specobjid, pca.specobjid, sp.plate,sp.mjd,sp.fiberid,sp.z as redshift, sp.zErr as redshift_err, sp.z_noqso, sp.zErr_noqso, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp, sp.veldisperr as sp_vdisp_err, pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, pca.vdisp_err as pca_vdisp_err FROM SpecObj AS sp JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objid = sp.bestobjid JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON sp.specobjid = pca.specObjID WHERE (sp.plate = # and sp.mjd = # and sp.fiberid = #)
